  <title><custom ref="synthesis-leccion-titulo"/></title>
  <title component="profesor"><nbsp/>([@@@@@@@@@] mins)</title>

  <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
  <p><q>Si les dan dos fracciones, ¿cómo pueden decidir si son equivalentes?</q> (I would look at diagrams of them to see if the fractions are the same size. I would use fraction strips to see if the fractions were the same size.)</p>

</subsubsection>



